Simple Weather App

A clean and simple Weather App built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript that shows real-time weather information for any city using the OpenWeatherMap API.

Features

Search weather by city name  
Displays temperature, weather condition, and weather icon  
Uses Fetch API to get live data  
Changes background color based on weather type (Sunny, Cloudy, Rainy, etc.)  
Shows an error message if city not found

Tech Stack

HTML5 – Structure of the page  
CSS3 – Styling and background gradients  
JavaScript (Vanilla)– Logic and API integration  
OpenWeatherMap API – Weather data source
